headline: Agilent Increases Cash Dividend to 24.8 Cents per Share
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., November 20, 2024--Agilent Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: A) today announced the company has increased its quarterly dividend to 24.8 cents per share of common stock, a 5% increase over the previous dividend. The quarterly dividend will be paid on Jan. 22, 2025, to all shareholders of record as of the close of business on Dec. 31, 2024.

headline: Agilent 2024 Early Career Professor Award Presented to Adeyemi Adeleye
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., November 20, 2024--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) announced today that Adeyemi Adeleye, Ph.D., has received the Agilent 2024 Early Career Professor Award for his contribution to environmental health and sustainability, developing green analytical technologies, methods, or laboratory working environments. Dr. Adeleye is an assistant professor in the Department of Earth and Environmental Engineering at Columbia University.
